description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if all of the following occur during the San Antonio Spurs vs. Dallas Mavericks game originally scheduled for February 5, 2026, 8:30 PM ET:

-Cooper Flagg scores 25 or more points

-Victor Wembanyama scores 30 or more points

-P.J. Washington records 7 or more rebounds

-Stephon Castle records 7 or more assists

-Victor Wembanyama records 3 or more blocks

Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.

If the game is postponed, this market will remain open until the game has been completed.

If this game is canceled or postponed past February 19, 2026, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to “No”.

If a listed player does not participate for any reason in the San Antonio Spurs vs. Dallas Mavericks game originally scheduled for February 5, 2026, this market will resolve to “No”.

The resolution source will be the official NBA box score as published on NBA.com.
